<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="angry-adj">angry <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'æŋɡri/    美 /'æŋɡri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>发怒的；生气的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an angry young man
愤青</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher got angry that Jenny was late again.
詹妮又迟到了，老师很生气。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) angry about / at / over sth：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She always becomes angry about / at / over small things.
她总是为琐事生气。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) angry at / with sb(about / for sth)：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was angry with myself for making such a stupid mistake.
我生自己的气，犯了这样愚蠢的错误。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>angrily /'æŋɡrəli/ adv   </p></div>